spec_data.Name: perl-CPAN-Releases-Latest
spec_data.Description:
This Perl module constructs a list of all distributions on CPAN, by default
using the MetaCPAN API. The generated index is cached locally. It will let you
iterate over the index, either release by release, or distribution by
distribution.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 08:18:47 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Find latest release of all distributions on CPAN
